297
00:21:13,538 --> 00:21:14,761
<i>Yes,</i>

298
00:21:14,761 --> 00:21:17,638
<i>somehow it felt like a safe place.</i>

299
00:21:17,638 --> 00:21:21,072
<i>But that's where I saw it.</i>

300
00:21:21,072 --> 00:21:25,172
<i>Someone was digging up the child</i>

301
00:21:25,172 --> 00:21:28,205
