410
00:28:35,838 --> 00:28:40,838
He was the one who ordered
your father's illegal arrest and torture.

411
00:28:41,472 --> 00:28:43,205
I don't understand.

412
00:28:44,505 --> 00:28:46,905
Father was your fiancé. How could he...

413
00:28:46,905 --> 00:28:48,713
Back then,

414
00:28:48,713 --> 00:28:51,105
