434
00:30:08,605 --> 00:30:10,805
<i>The subscriber you've dialed is unavailable.</i>

435
00:30:19,305 --> 00:30:23,038
Why didn't you answer the phone?

436
00:30:25,772 --> 00:30:26,805
Young Beom.

437
00:30:26,805 --> 00:30:28,972
You know that stuff they're
talking about on that broadcast?

438
00:30:28,972 --> 00:30:30,705
It's all nonsense!

439
00:30:30,705 --> 00:30:35,138
You just need to trust me, okay?

440
00:30:36,072 --> 00:30:38,825
No matter what you did,

441
00:30:38,825 --> 00:30:41,338
I won't leave you, Uncle.

442
00:30:41,338 --> 00:30:42,938
Because

443
