448
00:31:05,005 --> 00:31:08,038
Do you know what I don't understand the most?

449
00:31:08,038 --> 00:31:10,638
My father died after being tortured? Yeah.

450
00:31:10,638 --> 00:31:12,972
Okay, fine. Let's say it was an accident.

451
00:31:12,972 --> 00:31:16,072
Then, it never should've
happened again, right?

452
00:31:16,072 --> 00:31:17,805
But then, again!

453
00:31:18,772 --> 00:31:22,005
You created another victim!

454
00:31:27,338 --> 00:31:30,305
- Young Beom...
- Please sincerely apologize

455
00:31:30,305 --> 00:31:31,625
