457
00:31:41,672 --> 00:31:43,305
Uncle,

458
00:31:44,938 --> 00:31:46,938
I'll stay by your side.

459
00:31:49,572 --> 00:31:53,238
I'll kneel and apologize with you.

460
00:31:53,238 --> 00:31:54,905
So, Uncle...

461
00:31:55,772 --> 00:31:57,972
Okay?

462
00:31:57,972 --> 00:32:00,038
Please!

463
00:32:06,377 --> 00:32:09,572
- He's here, quick!
- Could you give us a statement?

464
00:32:09,572 --> 00:32:11,705
Regarding Mr. Im Seok Man, do you admit
