473
00:32:53,308 --> 00:32:55,305
That's not like you.

474
00:32:56,105 --> 00:32:58,572
Reckless?

475
00:32:58,572 --> 00:33:01,072
I've waited 30 years for this.

476
00:33:07,205 --> 00:33:09,815
Back then

477
00:33:09,815 --> 00:33:11,905
and now,

478
00:33:11,905 --> 00:33:14,272
