482
00:33:21,605 --> 00:33:23,872
We were once friends

483
00:33:25,205 --> 00:33:27,805
for a brief moment, weren't we?

484
00:33:31,005 --> 00:33:33,405
You said

485
00:33:34,638 --> 00:33:37,438
what separated us then
was a misunderstanding, but it wasn't.

486
00:33:37,438 --> 00:33:42,772
Even without that, we would have
ended up on opposite sides, like now.

487
00:33:42,772 --> 00:33:44,905
Because

488
00:33:44,905 --> 00:33:47,072
I finally found out

489
00:33:47,072 --> 00:33:49,438
what kind of person you are.

490
00:33:52,772 --> 00:33:55,872
Once I came to know you, I finally saw

491
00:33:55,872 --> 00:34:00,705
