you inflicted on me back in school.

492
00:34:05,138 --> 00:34:07,538
It was fear.

493
00:34:08,405 --> 00:34:10,105
You were afraid

494
00:34:11,305 --> 00:34:12,972
that your father

495
00:34:12,972 --> 00:34:15,605
wouldn't acknowledge you.

496
00:34:15,605 --> 00:34:18,305
That you'd be abandoned.

497
00:34:18,305 --> 00:34:23,738
So when you mistook me for your father's son,
you trampled me and tried to break me.

498
00:34:31,772 --> 00:34:35,172
Don't take your delusions too far.

499
00:34:36,238 --> 00:34:39,305
What do you even know about me?

500
00:34:39,305 --> 00:34:42,605
