501
00:34:43,672 --> 00:34:46,405
I would have stayed by your side.

502
00:34:48,038 --> 00:34:50,272
But you're not that kind of person.

503
00:34:51,372 --> 00:34:55,038
You would never keep someone
who knows your weakness as a friend.

504
00:34:57,205 --> 00:35:00,072
That is the difference between you and me.

505
00:35:04,272 --> 00:35:06,405
Nevertheless...

506
00:35:14,138 --> 00:35:16,672
What are you up to?

507
00:35:16,672 --> 00:35:19,605
Admitting your wrongdoing

508
00:35:19,605 --> 00:35:21,638
