509
00:35:22,305 --> 00:35:24,105
It must be frightening.

510
00:35:24,105 --> 00:35:26,272
Especially for someone like you,
who has so much to lose.

511
00:35:26,272 --> 00:35:27,817
But

512
00:35:27,817 --> 00:35:30,038
if we're together,

513
00:35:30,038 --> 00:35:33,638
if we pay the price together,
wouldn't it be better?

514
00:35:34,705 --> 00:35:36,305
What do you say?

515
00:35:37,905 --> 00:35:40,705
Now, it's your turn to take my hand.

516
00:36:00,072 --> 00:36:01,705
I'll give my answer

517
00:36:03,338 --> 00:36:05,405
