521
00:36:19,238 --> 00:36:22,072
Witness, please be seated.

522
00:36:27,705 --> 00:36:30,857
You were the prosecutor
in the 7th case, correct?

523
00:36:30,857 --> 00:36:33,105
[Witness Stand]

524
00:36:33,105 --> 00:36:35,172
Yes, that's correct.

525
00:36:35,838 --> 00:36:37,738
Witness,

526
00:36:37,738 --> 00:36:42,605
