530
00:37:20,138 --> 00:37:21,872
How can you be certain?

531
00:37:21,872 --> 00:37:24,338
If something like that had happened,

532
00:37:25,172 --> 00:37:26,772
the defendant...

533
00:37:27,405 --> 00:37:31,105
the defendant would have
told me, his prosecutor.

534
00:37:31,105 --> 00:37:32,841
But

535
00:37:32,841 --> 00:37:35,672
there were no such complaints.

536
00:37:35,672 --> 00:37:39,738
Then do you believe Lee Yong Woo's claim

537
00:37:39,738 --> 00:37:43,238
that he is the true killer
of the 7th case is false?

538
00:37:46,338 --> 00:37:49,405
It would need investigation,

539
00:37:50,705 --> 00:37:54,238
but in the case of serial killers,

540
00:37:54,238 --> 00:37:59,005
they often make false statements like that.

541
00:37:59,005 --> 00:38:02,238
For serial killers like Lee Yong Woo,

542
00:38:02,238 --> 00:38:05,538
their murder record is almost like

543
00:38:06,505 --> 00:38:09,005
a badge of achievement.

544
00:38:09,005 --> 00:38:11,113
The one who kills more

545
00:38:11,113 --> 00:38:13,005
becomes "number one."

546
00:38:13,005 --> 00:38:17,838
So they may falsely confess

547
00:38:17,838 --> 00:38:20,405
to crimes they did not commit.

548
00:38:20,405 --> 00:38:23,172
It could be seen as a need to show off.

549
00:38:28,205 --> 00:38:31,538
Finally, is there anything else
you'd like to say?

550
00:38:39,372 --> 00:38:41,238
Recently,

551
00:38:42,005 --> 00:38:45,105
an unverified media outlet

552
00:38:45,105 --> 00:38:50,838
has been spreading outrageous allegations.

553
00:38:50,838 --> 00:38:52,905
So I've been thinking.

554
00:38:52,905 --> 00:38:54,945
Why should I

555
00:38:54,945 --> 00:38:58,705
endure such humiliation?

556
00:38:58,705 --> 00:39:01,705
Yes, we failed to catch
the killer at the time.

557
00:39:01,705 --> 00:39:04,905
Some may see that as a failure.

558
00:39:04,905 --> 00:39:06,505
However,

559
00:39:07,805 --> 00:39:10,249
out of the millions of prosecutors

560
00:39:10,249 --> 00:39:12,505
and police officers

561
00:39:12,505 --> 00:39:14,472
assigned to that case,

562
00:39:14,472 --> 00:39:17,838
not a single one conducted the investigation

563
00:39:17,838 --> 00:39:19,472
without risking their lives.

564
00:39:19,472 --> 00:39:22,805
In fact, there were times we rescued victims,

565
00:39:23,672 --> 00:39:26,338
and I myself was stabbed with a knife

566
00:39:26,338 --> 00:39:30,972
and hovered between life and death for days.

567
00:39:30,972 --> 00:39:34,572
Even if I were to face that situation again,
I would do the same.

568
00:39:34,572 --> 00:39:37,905
That is my sincere belief.

569
00:39:40,072 --> 00:39:41,705
Well...

570
00:39:43,938 --> 00:39:46,377
If you just trust us
and wait a little longer,

571
00:39:46,377 --> 00:39:48,938
