574
00:40:01,605 --> 00:40:03,305
That's all.

575
00:40:10,538 --> 00:40:12,738
Your testimony today was flawless.

576
00:40:12,738 --> 00:40:15,372
I think you can rest easy now.

577
00:40:15,372 --> 00:40:17,638
Honestly, I'm disappointed.

578
00:40:21,138 --> 00:40:23,805
Excuse us for a moment.

579
00:40:29,372 --> 00:40:31,572
I know this isn't easy.

580
00:40:32,472 --> 00:40:36,272
As an assemblyman, admitting fault
and asking for forgiveness

581
00:40:36,272 --> 00:40:38,605
