582
00:40:38,605 --> 00:40:41,205
That's why it takes even more courage.

583
00:40:49,505 --> 00:40:52,405
I only need you.

584
00:40:52,405 --> 00:40:54,838
I don't need anything else.

585
00:40:57,305 --> 00:40:59,905
Then you should've made a different choice.

586
00:41:01,105 --> 00:41:04,538
I answered according to my principles.

587
00:41:04,538 --> 00:41:06,505
I did what I believed was right.

588
00:41:06,505 --> 00:41:11,005
That recognition is what brought me
to where I am now.

589
00:41:11,005 --> 00:41:13,338
Assemblyman, I will thoroughly

590
00:41:14,405 --> 00:41:17,005
verify everything you just said.

591
00:41:18,438 --> 00:41:21,372
I will never forget the care and support
you've given in raising me.

592
00:41:22,438 --> 00:41:25,105
From now on, I'll visit you
as Reporter Cha Young Beom.

593
00:41:50,505 --> 00:41:52,305
Your Honor,

594
00:41:52,305 --> 00:41:54,889
we request Lee Yong Woo, the real killer
of the Kangseng Serial Murder Case,

595
00:41:54,889 --> 00:41:57,505
as a witness.

596
00:42:27,772 --> 00:42:29,005
[Witness Stand]
Mr. Lee Yong Woo,

597
00:42:29,005 --> 00:42:33,238
you claimed that you're the real killer
of the seventh case.

598
00:42:33,238 --> 00:42:36,905
