603
00:42:52,405 --> 00:42:53,641
No,

604
00:42:53,641 --> 00:42:55,738
I just want to be certain.

605
00:43:06,038 --> 00:43:09,138
To enhance the credibility of your statement,

606
00:43:09,138 --> 00:43:13,638
