remembered through your senses.

607
00:43:13,638 --> 00:43:15,398
What you saw that day,

608
00:43:15,398 --> 00:43:16,705
what you heard,

609
00:43:16,705 --> 00:43:19,205
and things you touched with your hands.

610
00:43:24,872 --> 00:43:26,638
That room.

611
00:43:28,238 --> 00:43:30,105
Would you like me to draw it?

612
00:43:46,905 --> 00:43:48,538
Here it is.

613
00:44:05,172 --> 00:44:06,805
Over there.

614
00:44:06,805 --> 00:44:08,272
[Main Gate]
I entered through the main gate,

615
00:44:08,272 --> 00:44:12,305
and then crouched down
in front of the wooden floor area.

616
00:44:12,305 --> 00:44:14,205
And I climbed up onto the porch,

617
00:44:14,205 --> 00:44:20,438
drilled a hole in the door,
and looked inside.

618
00:44:20,438 --> 00:44:22,838
Then I opened the door

619
00:44:22,838 --> 00:44:24,505
and went inside,

620
00:44:24,505 --> 00:44:26,705
and there was a low desk.

621
00:44:26,705 --> 00:44:27,738
[Desk]

622
00:44:27,738 --> 00:44:29,905
I stepped over it.

623
00:44:29,905 --> 00:44:34,405
Then I saw the child sleeping

624
00:44:35,038 --> 00:44:37,105
