625
00:44:38,172 --> 00:44:42,505
Her breathing was steady,
so she seemed to be in a deep sleep.

626
00:44:42,505 --> 00:44:44,572
So I felt relieved.

627
00:44:48,305 --> 00:44:51,209
We'll submit the report
describing the crime scene at the time

628
00:44:51,209 --> 00:44:53,572
as evidence.

629
00:45:07,972 --> 00:45:09,872
Witness,

630
00:45:09,872 --> 00:45:13,505
do you have anything
you'd like to say to the defendant?

631
00:45:24,338 --> 00:45:25,938
I am

632
00:45:26,738 --> 00:45:28,705
truly sorry.

633
00:45:32,938 --> 00:45:35,372
Because of what I did,

634
00:45:36,105 --> 00:45:39,772
an innocent person
was made out to be a murderer.

635
00:45:39,772 --> 00:45:41,738
I sincerely hope that my testimony today

636
00:45:41,738 --> 00:45:46,272
will expose those who framed
the defendant and lived in comfort,

637
00:45:46,272 --> 00:45:50,005
and that the wrongdoing of those

638
00:45:50,005 --> 00:45:55,038
who took away the child I killed
and concealed her fate

639
00:45:56,138 --> 00:45:58,538
from her family

640
00:46:00,705 --> 00:46:02,972
