664
00:48:47,738 --> 00:48:50,638
I'm glad the trial ended well.

665
00:48:51,272 --> 00:48:53,372
It's all thanks to you, Mr. Cha.

666
00:48:54,572 --> 00:48:55,753
Oh, right.

667
00:48:55,753 --> 00:48:59,105
How is the case regarding that child Hye Jin?

668
00:48:59,105 --> 00:49:03,238
We submitted a complaint against
the police officers who concealed the body,

669
00:49:03,238 --> 00:49:06,405
and indictment decisions will be made soon.

670
00:49:10,472 --> 00:49:14,738
You were found not guilty after 30 years.
How do you feel right now?

671
00:49:15,472 --> 00:49:19,205
I still can't believe it.

672
00:49:19,205 --> 00:49:21,605
The court has issued an official apology.

673
00:49:21,605 --> 00:49:23,772
Will you accept it?

674
00:49:23,772 --> 00:49:26,572
What did they do wrong?

675
00:49:26,572 --> 00:49:30,872
I haven't heard a single word
from those who truly owe me an apology.

676
00:49:31,505 --> 00:49:35,472
But if they show regret even now,

677
00:49:35,472 --> 00:49:36,809
I will still forgive them.

678
00:49:36,809 --> 00:49:43,497
- Can you tell us more?
- Is there anything you want to say to them?

679
00:49:58,272 --> 00:49:59,905
Ji Hye!

680
00:50:06,772 --> 00:50:09,105
Seok Man...

681
00:50:22,805 --> 00:50:24,938
Is it really you?

682
00:50:24,938 --> 00:50:27,438
Why have you aged so much?

683
00:50:27,438 --> 00:50:29,705
I'm sorry.

684
00:50:29,705 --> 00:50:31,338
All this time,

685
