I didn't even come visit you once.

686
00:50:36,138 --> 00:50:41,038
No, why are you apologizing?
I'm the one who's sorry.

687
00:50:42,089 --> 00:50:45,538
I shouldn't have let you go
like that back then.

688
00:50:45,538 --> 00:50:47,905
You're doing well, right?

689
00:50:48,705 --> 00:50:52,038
You haven't been struggling
because of me, right?

690
00:50:57,481 --> 00:50:59,072
This is...

691
00:50:59,072 --> 00:51:00,738
Tae Ho,

692
00:51:00,738 --> 00:51:03,538
