695
00:51:07,372 --> 00:51:10,105
Oh my, it's Tae Ho!

696
00:51:10,105 --> 00:51:12,672
Oh my, Tae Ho! You...

697
00:51:12,672 --> 00:51:17,472
When did that little kid grow up so big?

698
00:51:17,472 --> 00:51:19,438
You've been through so much.

699
00:51:23,040 --> 00:51:24,758
Heavens...

700
00:51:33,205 --> 00:51:38,338
<i>The retrial verdict for the 7th Lee Yong Woo
Serial Murder Case has finally been reached.</i>

701
00:51:38,338 --> 00:51:42,905
<i>Im Seok Man, who was falsely accused
as the killer and spent 20 years in prison,</i>

702
00:51:42,905 --> 00:51:44,838
<i>has been declared not guilty.</i>

703
00:51:44,838 --> 00:51:49,638
<i>He said he was deeply moved
that the truth was finally revealed</i>

704
00:51:49,638 --> 00:51:52,705
<i>more than 30 years after the incident.</i>

705
00:51:53,772 --> 00:51:55,538
What's all this?

706
00:51:55,538 --> 00:51:57,972
