732
00:53:25,193 --> 00:53:26,569
Here.

733
00:53:31,405 --> 00:53:32,905
What about you?

734
00:53:33,638 --> 00:53:37,038
Have you eaten?

735
00:53:37,038 --> 00:53:38,772
That's not...

736
00:53:43,638 --> 00:53:45,193
Yes,

737
00:53:45,193 --> 00:53:46,793
I have eaten.

738
00:53:47,538 --> 00:53:50,205
Make sure you eat properly.

739
00:53:50,205 --> 00:53:52,472
And take good care of your mother too.

740
00:53:52,472 --> 00:53:54,405
My mom's busier than I am these days.

741
00:53:54,405 --> 00:53:56,838
Yesterday she met Mr. Im Seok Man
and apologized to him.

742
00:53:56,838 --> 00:53:59,372
And today, she's gathering capable lawyers.

743
00:53:59,372 --> 00:54:02,005
Why lawyers?

744
00:54:02,005 --> 00:54:03,972
Because of you, Professor.

745
00:54:03,972 --> 00:54:06,705
You've got a lot of lawsuits
and complaints against you.

746
00:54:06,705 --> 00:54:09,505
My mom's in full battle mode these days.

747
00:54:09,505 --> 00:54:12,772
She looks ready to go after anyone
who even tries to mess with my uncle...

748
00:54:24,038 --> 00:54:25,738
Next time,

749
00:54:25,738 --> 00:54:27,705
I'll come on an empty stomach.

750
00:54:29,905 --> 00:54:31,538
Let's eat together.

751
00:54:32,172 --> 00:54:33,805
<i>Uncle.</i>

752
00:54:44,472 --> 00:54:47,172
Today is the last day I'll be coming here.

753
00:54:47,838 --> 00:54:50,038
From now on, someone else will take my place.

754
00:54:50,038 --> 00:54:51,472
Why?

755
00:54:51,472 --> 00:54:53,972
They say I'm also involved in this case,

756
00:54:55,005 --> 00:54:57,505
